reviewText: Very happy with the dvds and the service.
kids LOVED these movies.  I think we've seen them a million times now...and they are from ages 18 mos. to 7 years.

This box set is the best deal for just $20, which includes both Garfield Gets Real and Garfields Fun Fest! Garfield Get Real features Garfield in a full CGI animated film with amazing detail. Its also packed with seven bonus featurettes and two DVD-ROM Games.
My children and I loved the other Garfield movies but this one was contrived, convoluted and not very funny.
